works.description:
In this post I explain how I add LED  
lighting to my model buildings.

This is one of many of my original posts (text, but also including my  
photographs) that are being appropriated without permission and in  
violation of my copyright by the site
"newinteriordesignstyle2010.blogspot.

This post, and the general content of my blog, is focused on providing  
tips, techniques, and ideas related to the construction of my N scale
model  
train layout as well as model trains more generally.
